<div id="review_1594171073" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1594171073" />
    <a title="Nadine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3759963-nadine"><img alt="Nadine" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1611519518p2/3759963.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1594171073?book_show_action=true">Mar 29, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nadine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nadine" href="/user/show/3759963-nadine">Nadine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1594171073" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9002788317185858364">&quot;How can someone so wonderful do something so terrible?&quot; <br/><br/><br/>That ending!!!! What?! I cannot wait to get my hands on the next book. Only two left and I think we&apos;re finally going to get some answers. <br/>The Grim Grotto is action packed. The Baudelaire&apos;s find themselves on a submarine then in a grotto with poisonous mushrooms only to be left wondering what to do next and who to trust. <br/><br/>Full series review: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://todaysechos.wordpress.com/2016/04/11/a-series-of-unfortunate-events-by-lemony-snicket/'>https://todaysechos.wordpress.com/201...</a></span>
  <span id="freeText9002788317185858364" style="display:none">"How can someone so wonderful do something so terrible?" <br /><br /><br />That ending!!!! What?! I cannot wait to get my hands on the next book. Only two left and I think we're finally going to get some answers. <br />The Grim Grotto is action packed. The Baudelaire's find themselves on a submarine then in a grotto with poisonous mushrooms only to be left wondering what to do next and who to trust. <br /><br />Full series review: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://todaysechos.wordpress.com/2016/04/11/a-series-of-unfortunate-events-by-lemony-snicket/">https://todaysechos.wordpress.com/201...</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="9002788317185858364" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

